<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/becky-edwards> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Becky Edwards joined the Further Education (FE) Commissioner team in 2020 as an FE Adviser. She was appointed Deputy FE Commissioner in September 2023. She is a qualified accountant and has a master’s degree in financial management. She has worked in senior finance roles in the FE sector for over 25 years, including: Executive Director of Finance, City of Bristol College Executive Director of Finance, Strode College"@en .
